data.description: Welcome to this inviting home! You won't want to miss out on the spacious open floor plan, boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The converted garage, which has been permitted, offers an excellent game room for your enjoyment. Experience the covered backyard patio, which overlooks the oversized backyard complete with a dog run. The mature trees provide ample shade, and you'll even find lemon and pomegranate fruit trees on the property. With plenty of opportunity, this home is waiting for you to make it your own. Conveniently located just minutes away from Wells Park and Hinman Elementary School. Call for appointment today.
